
= “a web-based social network that you use in your browser, without a central server… built on the power of Bittorrent.”

URL = http://vole.cc/


=Description=

"what if someone came up with a system that removed the need for massive centralized servers? That's just what vole.cc is working to accomplish. Vole.cc is a decentralized social media system in development based on bittorrent and Ember.js which completely cuts the server out of the equation and allows users to build social media networks without exposing their personal information to "authorities" or data mining companies."
(http://scgnews.com/6-anti-nsa-technological-innovations-that-may-just-change-the-world)


